# No Man's Sky Wiki Scraper Project Structure

This project scrapes data from the No Man's Sky wiki and stores it in structured formats.

## Core Files

- [nms_wiki_scraper.py](mdc:nms_wiki_scraper.py) - Main scraper class with MediaWiki API integration
- [nms_export.py](mdc:nms_export.py) - Export utility to convert SQLite data to JSON files
- [requirements.txt](mdc:requirements.txt) - Python dependencies
- [nms_data.db](mdc:nms_data.db) - SQLite database storing scraped data
- [data/](mdc:data/) - Directory containing exported JSON files

## Key Components

The `NMSWikiScraper` class handles:
- MediaWiki API requests with rate limiting
- Wiki markup parsing (infoboxes, crafting recipes, descriptions)
- SQLite database storage with deduplication
- Category-based scraping with manual grouping

## Data Flow

1. Scraper fetches wiki pages via MediaWiki API
2. Parses wiki markup into structured data
3. Stores in SQLite database with deduplication
4. Export script converts to grouped JSON files

## Database Schema

Items table contains: id, title, description, type, infobox (JSON), crafting (JSON), categories (JSON), source_category, group_name, timestamps.